BR23C uses lithium-polymer batteries that are lighter and more energy density, which means their life is longer than the lithium-ion version.
According to Andoh, instinctive intelligent reaction is important, not the ability to process data, even less to store.
This structure needs to process and respond to only a few input signals per second.
