There is no need for gigabyte or megabyte memories.
This is the first step towards the development of immediate avoidance technology, which, according to Nissan’s estimates, will be involved in series cars within ten years.
Additional application option may be the integration of the unit with the GPS satellite navigation system to drive the car to the specified end destination by avoiding obstacles on the road.
